name: RELEASED
description:
–
EDITION LIMITED TO 30 PRINTS.
–
PRINTS ARE UNFRAMED. FRAMING OPTIONS CAN BE PROVIDED ON REQUEST. PRINTS WILL HAVE A 70MM WHITE BORDER FOR MOUNTING AND FRAMING PURPOSES.
–
PRINTED ON HAHNEMÜHLE WILLIAM TURNER 310 GSM STOCK, USING ARCHIVAL PIGMENTED ULTRACHROME K3 INKS FROM EPSON. 
–
ALL PRINTS ARE HAND SIGNED AND NUMBERED AND ARE AUTHENTICATED WITH THE HAHNEMÜHLE CERTIFICATE OF AUTHENTICITY, INCLUDING NUMBERED HOLOGRAMS ON THE BACK OF THE ARTWORK AND THE CERTIFICATE.
–
SHIPPING COST INCLUDES INSURANCE AGAINST DAMAGE OR LOSS.
